          "text": "1. Overview"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The stored procedure "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "usp_ActiveAccountsByAgency",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " is designed to generate a report of active accounts associated with a specific agency, identified by the agency's code. It retrieves detailed information about these accounts, including their status, associated facilities, and utility service details. The procedure also logs the usage of the report for auditing purposes."
        }
